description: Demolition of warehouse buildings and redevelopment to provide two mixed use buildings of 8 and 9 storeys (to a maximum height of 31.5m) comprising 173 residential units, 2117sq.m of B1 office space, 107sq. m A3 cafe, and 2607sq.m basement area containing 20 disabled parking spaces and 228 cycle spaces and upgrade of adjacent 'Grotto Podiums' park.
